 of these drugs and in whom toxicity symptoms may be easily overlooked.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/86105/', '', 'Desvenlafaxine, St. John''s Wort, Nefazodone, Oxitriptan, Viloxazine, Vortioxetine, Milnacipran, Tryptophan, Levomilnacipran, Vilazodone, Esketamine, More', 'Alosetron, Isometheptene', 1767369485);
